    - port koji se  bude vrtio isto nek vuče iz .env
    - i kreiraj doc/ folder i reci mu nek unutra uvijek piše dokumentaciju štoi je radio
  
Kako pokrenuti Cline:
  - Prvo treba pokrenuti LiteLLM uz pomoć ove komande: litellm --model mistral/mistral-large-latest
  - Potencijalno prije toga treba postaviti API key komandom, ali mislim da se to ne koristi: $env:MISTRAL_API_KEY="ovdje_ide_moj_api_key"

Što sam još sređivao:
  - Run this command in powershell as admin: Set-ExecutionPolicy -Scope CurrentUser -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned
    - Allows PowerShell scripts that are created on your local machine to run without needing a digital signature.

Shortucts:
  - Ctrl/Alt+Enter = Toggle todo's box symbol
  - Alt+D = Toggle todo's done symbol
  - Alt+C = Toggle todo's cancelled symbol
  - Alt+S = Toggle a todo as started
  - Ctrl+Shift+A = Archive finished todos

